1. Clone the repository: `git clone <https://github.com/YlliM1/online_billing>`
2. Move the  folder to your XAMPP `htdocs` directory.
3. Start XAMPP and ensure Apache and MySQL are running.
4. 4. In the terminal on VS Code go to the folder you've taken, go to server subfolder, by typing cd server
5. In the `server` folder, run:
   - `npm install` to install dependencies.
4. In the terminal on VS Code go to the folder you've taken, go to client subfolder, by typing cd client
5. In the `client` folder, run:
   - `npm install` to install dependencies.
   - `npm start` to start the React development server.
6. (Important) The database needs to be exported by the creator of the web
